n, m, k, x, y = list(map(int, input().split()))

a = []
for i in range(1, n + 1):
	a.append(i)

b = []
for i in range(1, n + 1):
	b.append(n)

c = []
for i in range(1, m + 1):
	c.append(i)

a = sorted(a)
b = sorted(b)
c = sorted(c)

ans = 0
for i in range(x):
	ans += a[i]

for i in range(y):
	ans += b[i]

for i in range(n):
	ans -= c[i]

print(ans)
